## 📋 SQLi Testing Checklist

- [ ] Test GET parameters
- [ ] Test POST parameters
- [ ] Test Cookie values
- [ ] Test HTTP headers (User-Agent, Referer, X-Forwarded-For)
- [ ] Test JSON body parameters
- [ ] Test XML body parameters
- [ ] Check second-order SQLi (stored then executed)
- [ ] Test login forms
- [ ] Test search functionality
- [ ] Test ORDER BY / sort parameters

---

## 🧠 eWPTXv3 Tips

- Always try **second-order SQLi** — input stored then used in another query
- Test **JSON parameters** with SQLi payloads
- Look for **NoSQL injection** too (MongoDB: `{"$gt":""}`)
- Try **OOB SQLi** using Burp Collaborator
- Check **stored procedures** for injection
- Test **LIMIT/OFFSET** parameters

